      "message": "Pending Atlas extraction state renders a static yellow dot (&#9679;) with no spinner animation and no Turbo polling / meta-refresh. The requirements state: 'If Atlas extraction pending, spinner shown; polling via Turbo or page refresh.' Neither animate-spin nor any polling mechanism is present."
